data.oai_dc:dc: 1st column: the observation number (overall there is 127 observations), 2nd column: the identity of the individual, 3rd column: The day of the observation (1 to 89), 4th column: The observation: 1 to 5, 1 = Not breeding, 2 = Certainly breeding, 3 = Probably breeding, 4 = Possibly breeding, 5 = Undefined
